      <description>&lt;div&gt;I started a Pally last night and think I'm going to try and power level him up. All my other alts have had the slow grind. I'd take them out and do all the newbie quests. For a change I'm going to twink this toon a bit and try to get him some levels a little faster. I was going to work on 1Hs and 2Hs and skip the 1Hb and 2Hb. At least for now. I'll 2box this toon with my 61 Druid for awhile then use another alt later. Any advice since I've never power leveled a toon before?&lt;/div&gt;</description>
